umbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hY3tp4.png&h=678ff831&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UxiCxRK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUxiCxRK.png&h=5ce0ed8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ELk1ZBb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FELk1ZBb.png&h=b6b6cb16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qzEmZwK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqzEmZwK.png&h=a26b89ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">邊食大麻邊有賣鋪田贊助<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁賣鋪田啲粉有冇大麻</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7qsvSSb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7qsvSSb.png&h=4f2bdb39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同場仲有比人話樣裏就公審原post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2392261/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2392261/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">快啲加我fuckbook好友</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PJ6XxWA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPJ6XxWA.png&h=a70904f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QuDrrgB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQuDrrgB.png&h=01d1425f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AyOrrgA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAyOrrgA.png&h=02c46425&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QsbP8uW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQsbP8uW.png&h=b73d175d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T15:25:08.000Z","